Axiom.name: exOneRootThatMustBePlayed:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . exists n : Note . root((var c : Chord)) = n /\ hasAbsNote((var c : Chord), n)

Axiom.name: reltoabs_note:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord; n : Note . hasRelNote((var c : Chord), n) <=> hasAbsNote((var c : Chord), root((var c : Chord)) + n)

Axiom.name: dis1:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . not (root((var c : Chord)) = 1 /\ hasAbsNote((var c : Chord), 7) /\ hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 7))

Axiom.name: dis2:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . not (root((var c : Chord)) = 1 /\ hasAbsNote((var c : Chord), 2))

Axiom.name: dis3:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . not (root((var c : Chord)) = 1 /\ hasAbsNote((var c : Chord), 4) /\ hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 4))

Axiom.name: Ax6

Axiom.name: dis_minorMajorThird:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . not (hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 3) /\ hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 4))

Axiom.name: dis_perfectDimFifth:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . not (hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 7) /\ hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 6))

Axiom.name: dis_second:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . not hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 1)

Axiom.name: dis_seventhsixth:p:-1
Axiom.Text: forall c : Chord . not (hasRelNote((var c : Chord), x) /\ hasRelNote((var c : Chord), 9))

Axiom.name: AxSucc0-11:p:100:r:0
Axiom.Text: forall c : Note . suc(c) = 0 <=> (var c : Note) = x1

Axiom.name: AxSuccEql:p:100:r:0
Axiom.Text: forall c, d : Note . suc(c) = suc(d) <=> (var c : Note) = d

Axiom.name: AxSuccDontKnow:p:100:r:0
Axiom.Text: forall c : Note . c + 0 = (var c : Note)

Axiom.name: AxSuccAdd:p:100:r:0
Axiom.Text: forall c, d : Note . c + suc(d) = suc(c + d)
